name: Ready to Hei$$$t
description:
Mowie a.k.a The Goblin, the initiator from Alley Katz, now back on his hoods, Route 8O8. Having journey as lone wolf bomber in Main City is giving him a craziest idea to create a gang with Kimchee & Big Frank, his childhood friends.

Since he is the one who initiate to create the Alley Katz, so he's responsible to find the best HQ for 3 of them in Route 8O8. After a long searching & scouting the area, he set up the HQ in a abandoned building in the west area of Route 8O8. The outside of the building really doesn't look like there's a life in there, but if there's anyone have balls to enter and walk until 13th floor then it will see the different in there. Many tagging, piece, throw up, sticker slap, and everything that resemble "street culture" displayed in there.

No one knows where's the Alley Katz HQ is, but be sure if "No King" (reverse crown) sign appear, so it means the building is near.

Mowie, Kimchee, and Big Frank always hangout in there. Preparing big things that will blast a Main City in their next heist.

What kind of action they will do? We will see it as soon as possible.
